# Drone C2 Command Pipeline

Cloud-to-drone command & control (C2) over AWS. Commands flow from the cloud down to a PX4 drone via AWS IoT Core, a local MQTT broker, and a companion agent. Acknowledgements travel the same path in reverse. Every state transition is durable and ordered.

---

