## What's Next

Recommended build order:

1. End-to-end test of PX4 MAVLink commands (`RTL` / `LOITER` / `SET_MODE`) via agent
2. Implement agent heartbeat so the system treats the cloud link as alive/dead
3. Extend forwarder for reverse flow (cmd delivery + cmd_ack relay to IoT Core)
4. Deploy DynamoDB `Commands` table
5. Build SQS FIFO queue + Worker Lambda
6. Build Producer Lambda
7. Build `ack_processor` Lambda + IoT Rule
8. Add failsafe logic (RTL on link loss, geofence, watchdog Lambda)
9. Add cloud monitoring (ACK timeout alarms, no-telemetry alarms, CloudWatch C2 dashboard)
